description.narrative: DNDi is working on over 40 research projects including more than 20 new chemical entities in the following areas: 1. Drug discovery 2. Translational research 3. Clinical trials 4. Registration of drugs and access to treatments for neglected patients.

Since 2003, DNDi has addressed gaps in the traditional biomedical Research & Development system that lead to serious unmet medical needs for neglected patients. DNDi collaborates with global partners at all stages of the process to reduce illness, suffering, and death. To date DNDi has delivered nine new treatments for five deadly diseases saving millions of lives.
